skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: nonsense stories
des: Have you ever wanted to hear stories that make no sense? Here is your chance. You will be entertained with situations that just don't make sense, or stories so mundane that they don't need to be told again. Hear about the nonsensical adventures of Leah the Leopard, Black Bear, Deezy Deez Doze, and more. Just enable the skill and you will be transported to a world that nobody will understand.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
